com.tozny.e3db.android

Class AndroidConfigStore

  • Object
    • com.tozny.e3db.android.AndroidConfigStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigStore

    public class AndroidConfigStore
extends Object
implements ConfigStore
    Implements secure configuration storage. Uses the Android Key Store or a filesystem-based keystore to protect the configuration, depending on the key protection selected and the SDK level of the device.

        Parameters:

        protection - Protection used for securing the configuration. Cannot be null. If this uses the 'KeyAuthentication.KeyAuthenticationType.NONE' protection type, consider using thie AndroidConfigStore(Context) constructor instead.
        keyAuthenticator - Used to authenticate with the user when saving, loading or removing the key. Cannot be null.
